{
  "stem": "1020.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think, now, [NON-ENGLISH] 33, in Dabrowa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't go to Dabrowa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know for what reason, but it was very scary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Dabrowa didn't have many Jews before the war-- not as Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a Jewish city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So to go to Dabrowa was scary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I, I didn't trust, too much, the Poles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Being in the army, which I will turn a little bit back, which gets-- memories come back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was afraid for my Polish officers-- very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As much they could hurt, they did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because me-- they knew that I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I wouldn't-- I wasn't hiding anything to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And matter of fact, we have a sanitary officer in our battalion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was a surgeon already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If we were a few Jews, we kept our-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we stick together, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We both kept-- and, like, if we went out, if they go-- went Sunday to church, the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were trying to seek if it was-- where is a synagogue to see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But it was all closed up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Going-- the Russians closed up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The Germans destroyed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The Russians didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Communistic Poland, anti-Semites, they took it over for certain things for their benefits.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I lived in-- we lived in bunkers at the first line.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes, I was threatening-- was threatened to be-- with certain things as being a Jew, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some-- excuse me to express myself, which I shouldn't-- but some dumb Polack [LAUGHS] expressed his name-- his, his, his attitude.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He showed his attitude.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had-- I have pictures, which I-- a few of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember [NON-ENGLISH] and, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few names I can recall.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
